## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **ATTR amyloidosis modality 4-fold + 1 stabilizer (2018-2023)**: tafamidis (small-molecule tetramer stabilizer 2019) + patisiran (siRNA LNP 2018) + inotersen (ASO 2'-MOE 2018) + vutrisiran (siRNA GalNAc 2022) + eplontersen (ASO GalNAc 2023) + acoramidis 2024 (AG-10 small-molecule 2nd-gen stabilizer) → 6 ATTR therapeutics 5년만. RIBOZYME axis 의 가장 dense disease-target pair.
2. **mavacamten Camzyos 2022 first FDA cardiac myosin inhibitor** = small-molecule allosteric → ATP-independent muscle relaxation HCM. quantum-VQE 의 myosin allosteric pocket = hxq-iag-myosin-001 candidate motivation.
3. **omaveloxolone Skyclarys 2023 first FDA Friedreich ataxia** = Nrf2 activator. 30+ year Friedreich orphan disease → 첫 disease-modifying. quantum-VQE 의 KEAP1-Nrf2 PPI 표적.
4. **tofersen Qalsody 2023 first FDA SOD1-ALS** = accelerated approval (NfL biomarker, no clinical endpoint). historic ALS modality switch — RIBOZYME axis 가 ALS subtype-specific.
5. **inclisiran Leqvio 2021 PCSK9 siRNA twice-yearly** = compliance-favorable. quantum-VQE 의 PCSK9-LDLR PPI + ANGPTL3 (evinacumab) selectivity 비교 중요.
6. **HD tominersen FAILED Phase 3 2021** (Roche GENERATION-HD1) = HTT-lowering ASO 부작용 (NfL 증가 — neurotoxicity). HD AMT-130 AAV-mediated CNS delivery 가 next path. quantum-VQE 의 allele-selective ASO design 가 hxq-iag-htt-001 candidate motivation (CAG-expanded allele 만 selectively lower).
7. **Camzyos vs aficamten** — myosin inhibitor vs activator 의 mechanism 차이. cross-cardio.
8. **NTLA-2001 (Intellia) ATTR Phase 3 MAGNITUDE 진행** = first in-vivo CRISPR clinical (LNP-CRISPR-Cas9 hepatic, single dose). 2024 expanded enrollment. RIBOZYME + WEAVE cross-axis 의 합. quantum-VQE 의 Cas9-PAM-target seed 결합.
9. **PROTAC + LYTAC 성인 유전질환 적용** = CRBN E3 ligase + ASGPR-targeted degradation. quantum-VQE 의 ternary complex modeling 어려움 (RIBOZYME 의 boundary).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, inherited-adult 임상 의미 한정.

